snippet.title: Prison Boss Prohibition Mixed Reality Support Reveal | VR Games Showcase Spring 2025
snippet.description:
Wishlist Prison Boss Prohibition and learn more: https://linktr.ee/PrisonBossVRGS

The Quest version of Prison Boss Prohibition will come fitted out with a mixed reality mode playable in single-player or in co-op!

Welcome to New Yolk City! A wonderful place to live, except for the Mayor's harsh prohibition. Run various shops throughout the city, crafting and selling merchandise that's both strictly legal and questionably not, all to get super duper rich!
